casebody.data:
Keith BUFFARDI and Kendra Buffardi, Appellants,
v.
CITIZENS PROPERTY INSURANCE CORPORATION, Appellee. Case No. 5D18-2633 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Fifth District. Opinion filed February 22, 2019 Melissa A. Giasi, of Sivyer Barlow & Watson, P.A., Tampa, for Appellants. Jonathan D. Franklin, of the Franklin Legal Group, P.A., Miami, for Appellee. ON CONCESSION OF ERROR PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to Citizens Property Insurance Corporation's Concession of Error, we reverse the trial court's final judgment and remand for further proceedings.

REVERSED and REMANDED.

EVANDER, C.J., GROSSHANS and SASSO, JJ., concur.
